data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to this adorable condo in the heart of South Tampa with an assumable VA Loan! It is very important to note that this community has a wonderful HOA board and plenty of reserve funds! This stylish two-bedroom, two-bathroom condo offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Step inside and be greeted by new vinyl plank floors that seamlessly flow throughout the open-concept living space.    The condo boasts two generously sized bedrooms in a split floor plan. The master bedroom features an ensuite bathroom and large walk-in closet. The second bedroom is perfect for guests, a home office, or a cozy den, accommodating your every need.    But the allure of this condo doesn't end indoors – step outside onto your balcony and soak in the fresh air and open views. Enjoy your morning coffee or evening cocktails in this private outdoor space.    This condo comes with additional features that make everyday living a breeze. Stay comfortable year-round with the brand new air conditioner, and never worry about parking with your assigned parking space. Plus, indulge in the amenities of the community, including a sparkling pool and a relaxing jacuzzi. The perfect way to unwind and socialize with neighbors and friends.    Excitingly, the community is in the process of enhancing your living experience further – a brand new balcony is soon to be installed by the HOA.    Located in the highly sought-after South Tampa neighborhood, this condo offers the best of both worlds – a peaceful retreat and easy access to the vibrant city life and easy access to highway entrance. Enjoy nearby shopping, dining, and entertainment options, as well as beautiful parks and recreational areas.    Don't miss this great opportunity to own an upgraded condo in the heart of South Tampa. With its fantastic features, convenient location, and upcoming balcony upgrade, this property is a true gem. Schedule a viewing today! The Seller can easily accommodate a quick close!
